snippet.title: 3rd T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Sri Lanka | 30th July 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-india-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700000759

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 3rd and final T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India batted first and posted 137 runs for the loss of 9 wickets on a tough batting pitch. Sri Lanka started the chase well but lost their way when the Indian spinners came into play. Sri Lanka then kept losing wickets and the match ended in a draw. Finally, the game went into a super over and India sealed a thrilling victory to seal the series 3 - 0.

snippet.title: 1st T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Sri Lanka | 27th July 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-india-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700000759

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 1st T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India went all guns blazing and posted a massive total of 213 runs. Suryakumar Yadav was the top scorer with a vital 58 off 26 balls. Sri Lanka started the chase strongly however India picked up wickets in regular intervals and went on to win the match by 43 runs.

snippet.title: 2nd T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Sri Lanka | 28th July 2024
snippet.description:
India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 2nd T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. Sri Lanka started the batting well but lost their way towards the end. Sri Lanka managed to post 161 runs for the loss of 9 wickets. The match was later affected by rain and hence the target for India was 78 runs in 8 overs. India however showcased a superb batting performance and sealed a 7-wicket victory with 9 balls to spare.
.
.

snippet.title: Rahul Gandhi's 'Halwa' Attack, Nirmala's Viral Reaction: Budget, NEET, Agniveer, Jobs | Full Speech
snippet.description:
Leader of Opposition Rahul Gandhi attacked the Narendra Modi-led government in the Lok Sabha during the Union Budget 2024 debate. He displayed a photo from the "halwa ceremony," a traditional event at the Ministry of Finance before the budget presentation. Gandhi slammed Union Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman showing a photo of the Halwa Ceremony. Showing the picture he said, "The photo shows the distribution of Budget ka halwa. I don’t see any OBC, tribal, or Dalit officers here. While the country’s resources are being divided, 73% of the population is missing. The budget was prepared by 20 officers, yet it's being distributed as if by 20 people." Watch the full video for details.

en-US.title: Rahul Gandhi's 'Halwa' Attack, Nirmala's Viral Reaction: Budget, NEET, Agniveer, Jobs | Full Speech
en-US.description:
Leader of Opposition Rahul Gandhi attacked the Narendra Modi-led government in the Lok Sabha during the Union Budget 2024 debate. He displayed a photo from the "halwa ceremony," a traditional event at the Ministry of Finance before the budget presentation. Gandhi slammed Union Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman showing a photo of the Halwa Ceremony. Showing the picture he said, "The photo shows the distribution of Budget ka halwa. I don’t see any OBC, tribal, or Dalit officers here. While the country’s resources are being divided, 73% of the population is missing. The budget was prepared by 20 officers, yet it's being distributed as if by 20 people." Watch the full video for details.

#RahulGandhi #NarendraModi #LokSabha #UnionBudget2024 #HalwaCeremony #MinistryOfFinance #NirmalaSitharaman #Budget2024 #OBC #Congress #BJP #ParliamentLive

Jaan Nisar Episode 37 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 27th July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mohsin Mirza
Writer: Rehana Aftab

Cast:
Danish Taimoor as Nosherwan Ghaznavi

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.description:
Maruthi Nagar Subramanyam Theatrical Trailer 

In Cinemas August 23rd.

Buckle up, because Maruthi Nagar Subramanyam has landed, and he's bringing the ultimate laugh riot!

Thabitha Sukumar Presents 

A Lakshman Kaarya's Flick 

Directed by Lakshman Karya, and produced by PBR Cinemas & Lokamaatre Cinematics, #MNS is not just a movie—it’s a rollercoaster of laughs, drama, and endless entertainment! If you thought the poster launch and singles were trending, wait until you see this trailer. It's packed with so much fun, excitement, and jaw-dropping moments, you might need to catch your breath!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Exclusive: FM Nirmala Sitharaman Replies To Tough Questions On Why She Raised Tax
snippet.description:
#BTBudgetRoundTable2024 #nirmalasitharaman #middleclassfamily #tax 
At the #BudgetRoundTable2024 conference, Rahul Kanwal, Executive Director, Business Today; Sourav Majumdar, Editor, Business Today and Siddharth Zarabi, Managing Editor, BTTV engaged in an insightful conversation with Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman. The discussion focused on the recent tax hikes on various asset classes, including stocks, futures and options (F&Os), and the indexation of real estate. FM Sitharaman explained that the tax increases are minimal and aimed at rationalizing the tax system across different asset classes. She emphasized that measures such as indexation in the real estate sector were taken to ensure fair treatment across asset classes. FM Sitharaman assured that tax simplification remains a priority despite new changes, highlighting the GST's role in streamlining the tax structure nationwide. She clarified the hikes from 10% to 12.5% on stocks are not intended to boost government revenue but to achieve a more balanced tax framework. The government's aim is to maintain stability while simplifying taxes for broader economic equity.


#taxes #equity #governmentbudget 
-----------------------
Thank You for watching! Do not forget to Like | Comment | Share 
-----------------------

Watch us for the best news and views on business, stock markets, crypto currencies, consumer technology, the world of real estate, bullion, automobiles, start-ups and unicorns and  personal finance. #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:
* Monday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Tuesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Wednesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Thursday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Friday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Saturday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Sunday Tamil Devotional Songs

Special Devotional Collections:
* Shiva Tamil Devotional Songs: Celebrate the power and grace of Lord Shiva.
* Vishnu Tamil Devotional Songs: Immerse in the blessings of Lord Vishnu.
* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.
* Balaji Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship Lord Venkateswara with these soulful songs.
* Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Attract prosperity with hymns for Goddess Lakshmi.
* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.
* Vinayagar Tamil Devotional Songs: Devotions for the remover of obstacles, Lord Vinayagar.
* Ganapathi Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke blessings from Lord Ganapathi.
* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.
* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.

snippet.title: Superstar Singer S3 | Baarish Special | Ep 37 | Full Episode | 20 Jul 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 37: Baarish Special
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The contestants revel in the monsoon spirit with timeless Bollywood tunes that embody the magic of the rainy season. 

Show Name: Superstar Singer Season 3
Episode: 37
Super-Judge: Neha Kakkar
Captains: Pawandeep Rajan, Arunita Kanjilal, Salman Ali, Mohd. Danish, Sayali Kamble
Host: Harsh Limbachiyaa, Rohanpreet Singh
Director: Sahil Chhabria

#SuperstarSinger3 #सुपरस्टारसिंगर3 #setindia #nehakakkar #pawandeeprajan #arunitakanjilal #salmanali #mddanish #sayalikamble #harshlimbachiyaa #rohanpreetsingh 

Songs - Megha Re Megha Re, Dola Re Dola, Sayaani, Khari, Barsaat, Arjun & Nanis Theme, Ve Fukrey, Ek Ladki Bheegi Bhagi Si, Cocktail, Ve Fukrey, Kukkad, Rimjhim Gire Sawan, O Sajna Barkha Bahar Aayi, Kar Gayi Chull, Aaj Mausam Bada Beimaan Hai, Chhoti Si Kahani Se, Lagi Aaj Sawan Ki, Ghanan Ghanan, Pyar Hua Iqrar Hua, Sawan Ka Mahina, 
Singers - Lata Mangehkar, Suresh Wadkar, Shreya Ghoshal, KK, Kavita Krishnamurthy, Mohammad Rafi, Asha Bhonsle 
Lyricists - Santosh Anand, Nusrat Badr,Shailendra, Anand Bakshi, Gulzar
Music Directors - Laxmikant-Pyarelal, Ismail Darbar, Salil Chaudhary,  RD Burman, Shiv Hari

Click here to Subscribe to SonyLIV: http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About Superstar Singer Season 3 : 
----------------------------------------------------------------
Superstar Singer' is back with Season 3! Exceptionally talented children from across India under the age of 15 showcase their musical prowess. With guidance from super-judge Neha Kakkar and captains Pawandeep Rajan, Arunita Kanjilal, Salman Ali, Mohd. Danish and Sayali Kamble, the contests gain valuable insights from Neha Kakkar and guidance from the captains, ultimately growing as performers.

Click here to watch all the videos of Superstar Singer Season 3: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzufeTFnhupzoaX-zSdVecO8yhtebgvB0

snippet.description:
Get ready to move to the beats! Presenting the First Banger "Hauli Hauli" from The Much-Awaited Film "Khel Khel Mein". Starring Akshay Kumar, Ammy Virk, Taapsee Pannu, Vani Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Aditya Seal & Pragya Jaiswal. Sung by Guru Randhawa, Yo Yo Honey Singh and Neha Kakkar, Composed & Written by Guru Randhawa. Choreographed by Piyush-Shazia.

Gulshan Kumar, T-Series & Wakaoo Films Present
A T-Series Films, Wakaoo Films & KKM Film Ltd. Production

snippet.title: SUPNA (Official Video) | JOBAN SANDHU | GEET GORAYA | Latest Punjabi Songs 2024
snippet.description:
Introducing the official video of Joban Sandhu's new punjabi song Supna in which the music is given by Abhijit Baidwan. We're excited to share our music with the world. We hope you enjoy listening to it as much as we enjoyed creating it ;)
Do listen & Don't Forget to Leave your valuable Comments :)
#punjabisong #latestpunjabisongs #tseries 

Song: Supna
Singer: Joban Sandhu
Female Lead: Geet Goraya
Music: Abhijit Baidwan
Lyrics: Fateh Shergill
Director: Hitesh Arora
Music Label: T-Series

Lyrics - 

Tere Naal naal reh ke, main ummar langauni aa, koi aakhri isha puche je tere naal jiyoni aa,
Mere dil de vehre aan ke karwayi tu dhan dhan ve, 
Main Supna te nahi vekhdi yan sachi chadea chann ve-2, 
Tera Vehndiyan hanian main wangan layian bhann ve,
Main Supna Te nahi vekhdi han sachi chadea chann ve….

1- Duniyan ton luko ke rakhna main, tainu toom bana k sajjna ve,
Akhiyan cho’n nikle surme te ajj ton naa tera hi lagna ve, 
Mainu ron deyi’n na sohneya kite nazran kar ke gair ve,
Tainu rabb di thaanve’n poojdi main din de chaare pehar ve, 
Main khaira’n mang mang rakhdi chuniian de palle bann ve, 
Main Supna…….

2- Sajjna Barkat hi barkat aa tainu mathe lawan uthdi main, 
Khiyalan wich tere sirr utton main nazran laah laah sutdi main,
Tere naal krke haye matchinga poore krne armaan ve,
Main teri channa walea tu mera shah sultan ve, 
Main Fateh manan lakh terian tu bhawen ik na mann ve, 
Main Supna….

3- Main rahan gawachi sohneya mainu gharde jhalli kehan mere, 
Tu masa masa hi dikhdan e yan jhalle ho gaye nain mere,
Main kothe charh charh vekhdi phirni ton murhu teri thaar ve,
Main teri khatir sajdi ne suit badal laye chaar ve,
Mera haar shingar tu souneya bhawen duniya wann suwann ve…
Main Supna….

Tere Naal naal reh ke, main ummar langauni aa, koi aakhri isha puche je tere naal jiyoni aa,
Mere dil de vehre aan ke karwayi tu dhan dhan ve, 
Main Supna te nahi vekhdi yan sachi chadea chann ve-2, 
Tera Vehndiyan hanian main wangan layian bhann ve,
Main Supna Te nahi vekhdi han sachi chadea chann ve….

1- Duniyan ton luko ke rakhna main, tainu toom bana k sajjna ve,
Akhiyan cho’n nikle surme te ajj ton naa tera hi lagna ve, 
Mainu ron deyi’n na sohneya kite nazran kar ke gair ve,
Tainu rabb di thaanve’n poojdi main din de chaare pehar ve, 
Main khaira’n mang mang rakhdi chuniian de palle bann ve, 
Main Supna…….

2- Sajjna Barkat hi barkat aa tainu mathe lawan uthdi main, 
Khiyalan wich tere sirr utton main nazran laah laah sutdi main,
Tere naal krke haye matchinga poore krne armaan ve,
Main teri channa walea tu mera shah sultan ve, 
Main Fateh manan lakh terian tu bhawen ik na mann ve, 
Main Supna….

3- Main rahan gawachi sohneya mainu gharde jhalli kehan mere, 
Tu masa masa hi dikhdan e yan jhalle ho gaye nain mere,
Main kothe charh charh vekhdi phirni ton murhu teri thaar ve,
Main teri khatir sajdi ne suit badal laye chaar ve,
Mera haar shingar tu souneya bhawen duniya wann suwann ve…
Main Supna….

snippet.title: Prem Nu Sagpan - 4K Video - Vikram Thakor - Saloni Thakor - Latest Gujarati Song 2024
snippet.description:
Song: Prem Nu Sagpan
Singer & Artist: Super Star Vikram Thakor
Singer: Saloni Thakor
Artist: Sudha Tripathi
Music: Vishal Vagheshwari
Lyrics: Ramesh Vachiya
D.O.P.:  Sehzad Mansuri (Tipu)
Edit:  Naresh Rajput
Concept & Director: Farukh Gayakwad
Producer: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics Of This Song:

Ho... Gori Re...
Ho... Valamiya...
Ho Ho Ho... Gori Re...
Ho... Valamiya...

Ho Bhulati Na Re Prem Thi Bandhyu, Prem Nu Hagapan Chhe
Bhulti Na Re Prem Thi Bandhyu, Prem Nu Hagpan Chhe
Yaad Rakhje Gori Taru Gomade Pan Koi Chhe
Ho Dhadakta Aa Dil No Ek Tu Dhabkaro Chhe
Dhadkta Aa Dil No Aek Tu Dhabakaro Chhe
Kem Re Bhulu Valam Tu Mara Jiv Thi Vhalo Chhe
Ho... Jay Chhe Chhodi Pardesh Tu Aavaje Veli Deh Ma
Vatyu Jova Ma Pran Na Jay Joje Mara Neh Ma
Ho Ven Na Bol Kadava Valam Dalade Mara Vage Chhe
Ven Na Bol Kadva Valam Dalde Mara Vage Chhe
Chhella Mara Swas Sudhi Prit Tari Mange Chhe
Ho Yad Rakhje Gori Taru Gomde Pan Koi Chhe


Ho Padar Na Pipade Mane Khobale Poni Pati
Sathe Rehvana Kol Didha Ta Bhuli Na Re Jati
Ho Ho... Evo Vichar Karsho Nahi Tamne Bhuli Jaishu
Kathan Kalaja Kari Valam Juda Thai Ne Rahishu
Ho Mane Chhodi Jata Shid Upadashe Pag Tara
Tara Vagar Rokai Jashe Dil Na Re Dhabkara
Ho Jiv Nathi Dur Thavano Aa Karame Dado Chhe
Jiv Nathi Door Thavano Aa Karme Dado Chhe
Kem Re Bhulu Valam Tu Mara Jiv Thi Valo Chhe
Ho... Yad Rakhaje Gori Taru Gomade Pan Koi Chhe


Ho Valaje Vali Veli Joje Modu Na Re Thay
Jiravashe Nai Tari Judai Jiv Maro Lai Jay
Ho O... Aavu Na Re Bolo Valam Aankh Radi Jay
Tari Chhu Ne Tari Revani Tane Kem Bhulay
Ho... Cham Re Vali Tane Mara Dukh Na Dekhay Chhe
Eklo Mane Meli Kem Pardesh Tu Jay Chhe
Ho Valashu Vela Pachha Ame Malashu Vala Tamane
Valshu Vela Pachha Ame Malshu Vala Tamne
Josho Mari Vat Re Vala Khailo Mara Ham Re
Ho.. Jivashu Tari Yaad Ma Ame Vali Tara Ham Re
Ho.. Dalade Valam Tamne Rakhya Viharashe Nai Vhal Re
